## Project Structure
The application follows a layered backend architecture:

- Auth Layer – Handles authentication logic
- DAO Layer – Database operations using JDBC
- Model Layer – Entity representations
- Admin Module – Order & delivery monitoring
- Database Layer – Centralized DB connection

SQL scripts are included separately for schema and data setup.
